

? Baumgardner ist ein Mit-Begründer der → biblisches/Flut/Katastrophische-Plattentektonik[katastrophischen Plattentektonik].

{ Plattentektonik

  John Baumgardner versucht, den → Mythologie/Plattentektonik[Mythos der Plattentektonik] mit der Bibel in Einklang zu bringen:
  "
     Henry Morris visited the church I was attending many years
     ago to promote creation and the flood. I decided to focus on
     problems in earth science.
     -
    *I had an epiphany. We must figure out how to fit plate tectonics into the Bible.*
  " [ John Baumgardner, 7. August, 2013, 7. ICC ]

}
